---
import { ArrowLeft, ArrowRight, Tag, Calendar } from 'lucide-astro';

---
<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 overflow-hidden"><div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto"><div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-12"><div><p class="text-[#78BE20] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] mb-2">Conocimiento y tendencias</p><h2 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Dale un vistazo a nuestro Blog</h2><div class="w-14 h-1 bg-[#78BE20] mt-4 rounded-full"></div></div><div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-3"><button class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 border-gray-200 text-gray-300 cursor-not-allowed"><ArrowLeft class="lucide lucide-arrow-left w-5 h-5" /></button><button class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 border-[#0F2E65] text-[#0F2E65] hover:bg-[#0F2E65] hover:text-white cursor-pointer"><ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-5 h-5" /></button></div></div><div class="relative"><button class="md:hidden absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-2 z-10 w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 pointer-events-none"><ArrowLeft class="lucide lucide-arrow-left w-4 h-4 text-[#0F2E65]" /></button><button class="md:hidden absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-2 z-10 w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 opacity-100"><ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 text-[#0F2E65]" /></button><div class="flex gap-6 overflow-x-auto snap-x snap-mandatory scroll-smooth pb-4 -mr-4 pr-4" style="scrollbar-width: none;"><div class="group flex-shrink-0 w-[90%] md:w-[85%] lg:w-[calc(100%-120px)] snap-start rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-500 bg-[#F8FAFC]"><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[480px]"><div class="lg:w-[45%] relative overflow-hidden"><img alt="Eventos Masivos" class="w-full h-56 lg:h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="/assets/asset_3.jpg"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,transparent_70%,#F8FAFC_100%)] hidden lg:block"></div></div><div class="lg:w-[55%] flex items-center"><div class="p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5"><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 text-[#0F2E65] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold"><Tag class="lucide lucide-tag w-3 h-3" />Eventos</span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gray-400 text-xs"><Calendar class="lucide lucide-calendar w-3 h-3" />Mayo 2025</span></div><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight leading-tight">Eventos Masivos</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 line-clamp-5">En los grandes festivales musicales como los que reúnen a decenas de miles de personas durante varios días la tecnología es el motor silencioso que permite que todo funcione. Detrás de los escenarios, la operación digital sostiene desde la venta de accesos y los sistemas de pago hasta las comunicaciones del staff, la vídeo vigilancia y la logística en tiempo real. Cuando la visibilidad del evento es alta y la demanda se dispara, la ciberseguridad y la conectividad dejan de ser un soporte para convertirse en un elemento crítico.</p><button class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-[#78BE20] text-[#78BE20] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#78BE20] hover:text-[#0F2E65] transition-all duration-300 group/btn">Leer Artículo<ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform" /></button></div></div></div></div><div class="group flex-shrink-0 w-[90%] md:w-[85%] lg:w-[calc(100%-120px)] snap-start rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-500 bg-[#F8FAFC]"><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[480px]"><div class="lg:w-[45%] relative overflow-hidden"><img alt="Ciberseguridad en la Nube" class="w-full h-56 lg:h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="/assets/asset_2.jpg"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,transparent_70%,#F8FAFC_100%)] hidden lg:block"></div></div><div class="lg:w-[55%] flex items-center"><div class="p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5"><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 text-[#0F2E65] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold"><Tag class="lucide lucide-tag w-3 h-3" />Seguridad</span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gray-400 text-xs"><Calendar class="lucide lucide-calendar w-3 h-3" />Abril 2025</span></div><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight leading-tight">Ciberseguridad en la Nube</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 line-clamp-5">La migración a la nube ha transformado la forma en que las empresas gestionan sus datos y operaciones. Sin embargo, esta transformación digital también ha abierto nuevas vías de ataque para los ciberdelincuentes. Descubre cómo proteger tu infraestructura cloud con estrategias de seguridad multicapa que combinan prevención, detección y respuesta en tiempo real.</p><button class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-[#78BE20] text-[#78BE20] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#78BE20] hover:text-[#0F2E65] transition-all duration-300 group/btn">Leer Artículo<ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform" /></button></div></div></div></div><div class="group flex-shrink-0 w-[90%] md:w-[85%] lg:w-[calc(100%-120px)] snap-start rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-500 bg-[#F8FAFC]"><div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch min-h-[400px] lg:min-h-[480px]"><div class="lg:w-[45%] relative overflow-hidden"><img alt="El Futuro del 5G Empresarial" class="w-full h-56 lg:h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" src="/assets/asset_1.jpg"><div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,transparent_70%,#F8FAFC_100%)] hidden lg:block"></div></div><div class="lg:w-[55%] flex items-center"><div class="p-8 md:p-10 lg:p-12"><div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-5"><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#0F2E65]/5 text-[#0F2E65] px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold"><Tag class="lucide lucide-tag w-3 h-3" />Tecnología</span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gray-400 text-xs"><Calendar class="lucide lucide-calendar w-3 h-3" />Marzo 2025</span></div><h3 class="text-[#0F2E65] text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight leading-tight">El Futuro del 5G Empresarial</h3><p class="text-gray-600 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 line-clamp-5">La tecnología 5G está revolucionando la conectividad empresarial con velocidades ultra rápidas y latencia mínima. Desde fábricas inteligentes hasta ciudades conectadas, el 5G habilita aplicaciones que antes eran imposibles. Conoce cómo esta tecnología puede impulsar la transformación digital de tu organización y abrir nuevas oportunidades de negocio.</p><button class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-2 border-[#78BE20] text-[#78BE20] px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:bg-[#78BE20] hover:text-[#0F2E65] transition-all duration-300 group/btn">Leer Artículo<ArrowRight class="lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1 transition-transform" /></button></div></div></div></div><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-4"></div></div></div><div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-8"><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium"><span class="text-[#0F2E65] font-bold">1</span> / 3</p><div class="flex items-center gap-2"><button class="h-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 w-8 bg-[#0F2E65]"></button><button class="h-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 w-3 bg-[#0F2E65]/25 hover:bg-[#0F2E65]/40"></button><button class="h-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-500 w-3 bg-[#0F2E65]/25 hover:bg-[#0F2E65]/40"></button></div></div></div></section>
